## Email Format

Both regular and LMP confirmations follow this order:

```
CONTRACT NO + type badge
Customer Name
Contract Received | Term
Credit Approved   | Contract Rate ($/kWh)
Executed          | Company Quote ($/kWh)
Forwarded         | Commission
AMERIPOWER LLC APPRECIATES YOUR BUSINESS
ESI-IDs | Broker Name
Tax Exempt
Type of Contract | Enrollment Type
Start Date
Load Profiles | Paper Bill Required
Customer Email (if present)
AmeriPower Mills (if present)
Comments (if present)
Auto-generated footer
```

---

## Prior Day Table Update Flow

When admin uploads any pricing table:

1. Current table data → copied to prior table (TRUNCATE prior + INSERT SELECT)
2. New data → inserted into current table

Tables covered:

- `heat_rates` → `prior_heat_rates`
- `consumption` → `prior_consumption`
- `margin` → `prior_margin`
- `tdsp` → `prior_tdsp`
- `txu` → `prior_txu`
- `gas_strip` → `prior_gas_strip`

